

     
      Planet Sun is an aggregation of public weblogs written by employees of Sun Microsystems. Tim Bray has been supportive of blogging inside and outside of the company, and now a new aggregator, Planet Sun, seems already to reflect a rising tide of blogs devoted to the main technologies fostered by the Santa Clara headquarters, including Java.  Hey guys, this site is worth the subscription.  [Resource-Type: Weblink; Category: Java/General; XRating: 4]
     
    
